        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/golden/mission_gecko/scene_gecko_basic.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 40e26dc7-bab2-4842-84d0-0283aaae8cd6).Image",
        "Description": "Good day, 47.\rYour targets are 3 security guards of the penthouse located at the top of the Burj Al Ghazali.\rThe repetitive harassment and violent behavior of the targets towards the staff caused a tense atmosphere at the penthouse. However, what made the clients, the workers themselves, truly enraged was the recent beating of one the staff members at the hands of these 3 guards.\rThe clients asked for an &quot;elegant but ruthless execution&quot;, surely you&apos;ll be able to satisfy their request.\rGood luck.",
